&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .25in? 0pt list tab-stops: lfo1; level1 l0 mso-list:&gt;&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?&gt;7.&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt Roman?? ?Times New&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;More shape changing forms and&amp;nbsp;ideally special abilities for each &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
