&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .25in? 0pt list tab-stops: lfo1; level1 l0 mso-list:&gt;&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?mso-list: Ignore?&gt;10.&lt;SPAN **Zowie**?FONT: 7pt Roman?? ?Times New&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;Regen spell line boosted especially at high levels &lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(done)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .25in? 0pt list tab-stops: lfo1; level1 l0 mso-list:&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: 0.25in; TEXT-INDENT: -0.25in; .25in? 0pt list tab-stops: lfo1; level1 l0 mso-list:&gt;&lt;SPAN red? **Zowie**?COLOR:&gt;Ky&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;B **Zowie**?mso-bidi-font-weight: normal?&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by Kytherea on &lt;span class=date_text&gt;05-09-2005&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=time_text&gt;10:29 AM&lt;/span&gt;</description>
