&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: justify; TEXT-ALIGN:&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;NOTE:&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt; Single target heal spells should be addressed in the next update scheduled for 5/11/2005.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: justify; TEXT-ALIGN:&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;1. Fix Exodus &lt;FONT color=#0033ff&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;(new)&lt;BR&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;- it goes off after reaching bindpoint after death, putting you at safe point in your bind zone&lt;BR&gt;- causes player to go LD, and not evac (thus resulting in death)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;&#xD;
