&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: justify; TEXT-ALIGN:&gt;The list:&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
