&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: justify; TEXT-ALIGN:&gt;- increase CoT cap to match new min. hynid levels in Vxed and Tipt (druids used to be able to charm the lower level animals there, but the recent revamping of those zones to increase XP by boosting mob levels stopped that)&lt;BR&gt;- need mobs to charm with OoW charm upgrade spell: remove uncharmable block on animals in previous expansions; add animals of suitable level in OoW. &lt;BR&gt;- tag mobs that should be animals as animals&amp;nbsp; (suggested list of mobs by zone being prepared)&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
