&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: justify; TEXT-ALIGN:&gt;- remove outdoor restriction on harmony (no change planned at this time)&lt;BR&gt;- the aggro/assist radii for harmony should match pacify &lt;BR&gt;- need upgraded harmony with higher level cap --&amp;gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; OoW spell should not have outdoor restriction since it no longer has any advantage over any other lull/pacify spell.&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
