&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: justify; TEXT-ALIGN:&gt;- druids should share Entrap as AA skill&amp;nbsp; (druids share Innate Camo and similar skills with rangers, and druids get various snares before rangers get comparable spells) &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(An entrap type AA may be added for druids in the future but there is no plan to do so right now.)&lt;/FONT&gt; - Some abilities may be shared between classes but not all are intended to be shared.&lt;BR&gt;- upgrade to AoE snare with resist modifier and greater speed reduction (so it is not overwritten)&lt;BR&gt;- fewer immune mobs &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(no change planned at this time)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: justify; TEXT-ALIGN:&gt;8. More shape changing forms and ideally special abilities for each &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
