&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: justify; TEXT-ALIGN:&gt;10. Improved run speed&amp;nbsp; &lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated)&lt;/FONT&gt; &lt;/P&gt;&#xD;
&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0pt; auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: mso-margin-top-alt: auto? 0in **Zowie**?MARGIN: justify; TEXT-ALIGN:&gt;- "Spirit of Horse":&amp;nbsp; faster SoW closer to run speed of higher end horse or&amp;nbsp; base Selo's,&amp;nbsp; with or without lev effects (floating effect of FoE causes motion sickness, excessive lag for many players)&lt;BR&gt;- faster SoW;&amp;nbsp; indoor SoW&lt;BR&gt;- revised Spirit of Cheetah spell (druid only, longer duration, no long recast time)&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
