&lt;P class=MsoNormal 0in 0pt; auto? mso-margin-top-alt: mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; **Oompa-Loompa**?MARGIN:&gt;&lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;&lt;SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: #cccccc?&gt;1.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Improve our healing abilities &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: red?&gt;&lt;FONT color=#ff0000&gt;(currently being evaluated) &lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;FONT face="Times New Roman"&gt;&lt;FONT size=2&gt;&lt;SPAN **Oompa-Loompa**?COLOR: red?&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;EM&gt;Specific examples:&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;EM&gt;&lt;/EM&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;EM&gt;- allow Healing Gift to apply to TR and KR&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;EM&gt;- remove % caps on TR/KR&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
